729813f-a.title: Richmond: Victory Boulevard - Hodges Place
729813f-a.text:
1649-1655 Victory Boulevard, at the N.E. corner of
Hodges Place (at the head of Todt Hill Road), showing the Castleton
Hi(l Moravian Church. In 1898 it was known as the Moravian Collegiate
Charch.and in 1907 as the United Brethen Church.
April, 1930
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTONS
